info.description:
ReportBro Library
=================

ReportBro is a library to generate PDF and Excel reports. The reports can be designed
with `ReportBro Designer <https://github.com/jobsta/reportbro-designer>`_,
a Javascript Plugin which can be integrated in your web application.

Demos can be found at https://www.reportbro.com.

Features
--------

* Python 2.7 and Python >= 3.5 support
* Generate pdf and excel reports
* Support header, footer and various page formats
* Use text, line, images and tables
* Evaluate expressions and display parameters
* Text and element styling

Installation
------------

.. code:: shell

    pip install reportbro-lib
